FBIS4-41785 "drsov124_h_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-124 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 Moldova Smugglers Caught Trying To Sell Radioactive Substance Smugglers Caught Trying To Sell Radioactive Substance LD2806055594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0500 GMT 28 Jun 94 LD2806055594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] According to information in the RABOCHAYA TRIBUNA a criminal group which tried to sell a container of radioactive substances exported from Russia for $20,000 has been detained by the police in Moldova. An expert investigation showed that the factory-made package, which was confiscated, contained gamma-cobalt-60. In spite of the fact that it had been hermetically sealed, the experts discovered a small leak of the radioactive substance.
